{"tid":411130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行山男大欖郊野公園暈低 送院不治","createTime":"2017-09-23T14:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T03:45:03.000Z","uid":34252,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e35185f1ac6b1a3676b0e4c6ea0b4d22fc7e64e","tid":411130,"uid":34252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:12:10.000Z","msg":"一行9人今早由荃灣川龍出發行山，目的地為大棠，至下午3時許，眾人經至大欖郊野公園內的大欖林道大棠段時，其中一名60歲姓王男子突然暈倒，友人見狀慌忙報案。消防及救護員趕至，事主已陷入昏迷，救護員替他做心外壓急救，其後由直升機送往東區醫院搶救，惜抵院後證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">救護員救治片段... 睇到好心酸</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P2TklNqiwTo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP2TklNqiwTo&d=CU0xZXF8PN25iZTvszaXNNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=54d18738\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P2TklNqiwTo</a>"},{"pid":"8ee0f0bb4f0f996727c19a84a3306a845f11d43b","tid":411130,"uid":124748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:16:18.000Z","msg":"廢老連行山都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b16da52baf4eca3c7c42e5a3d812ce4be5d467","tid":411130,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:16:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c542a8efd04a3d24052dd3586c3a79caff0c077","tid":411130,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d267b60a4a9918310375e6746997cd9c6a6442f","tid":411130,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢老連行山都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家啲50後，行少少路都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f757f2c7b5cc423c59a8676d9890c04deacba5e4","tid":411130,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0319ef0c8bacceac9e279e849d18b8b66f45d456","tid":411130,"u